# Description:
#   Energy-dependent interstellar X-ray extinction model,
#   including gas absorption, dust absorption, and dust scattering.
#   Element abundance      : Proto-Sun + Galactic Chemical Evolution.
#   Dust model             : silicate + graphite/PAHs.
#   Grain size model       : essentially exponentially-cutoff power-law 
#   size distributions for silicate and graphitic grains; log-normal size
#   distributions for PAHs.
#   For details, see Yan et al. (2026).
#  Columns:
#  1 Energy (eV)
#  2 Gas_abs (cm^2/H)
#  3 Dust_abs (cm^2/H)
#  4 Dust_sca (cm^2/H)
#  5 Total_ext(= gas absorption + dust absorption + dust scattering) (cm^2/H)   
